.TH "ath5k_hw_txpower" 9 "ath5k_hw_txpower" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ath5k_hw_txpower \- Set transmission power limit for a given channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" ath5k_hw_txpower
.BI "(struct ath5k_hw *ah "  ","
.BI "struct ieee80211_channel *channel "  ","
.BI "u8 txpower "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ah" 12
The \fIstruct ath5k_hw\fP
.IP "channel" 12
The \fIstruct ieee80211_channel\fP
.IP "txpower" 12
Requested tx power in 0.5dB steps
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Combines all of the above to set the requested tx power limit
on hw.
